        <h2>Legal & Oversight Partners</h2>
        <p>Our <strong>Independent Prison Oversight</strong> program collaborates with Arizona Capital Representation Project and the Federal Public Defender to monitor ADCRR's constitutional compliance. These attorneys provide pro bono support when we file emergency motions or interpret complex regulations. We've partnered with the University of Arizona School of Law to create a Prison Law Clinic where students assist with grievance analysis.</p>
        <p>For <strong>Core Civics & Advocacy Training</strong>, we partner with Arizona Advocacy Network and Local First Arizona to teach campaign finance law and small business development for returning citizen entrepreneurs. These partnerships ensure our graduates have political and economic power. We also work with the Phoenix Suns and Mercury on "Fair Chance Hiring" initiatives.</p>
